OctopusDeploy,is,an,automated,deployment,system,for,NET,The,scale,of,deployments,can,range,in,size,some,deploy,to,a,handful,of,servers,while,our,largest,installations,deploy,hundreds,of,projects,to,hundreds,of,servers,The,OctopusDeploy,API,uses,REST,calls,returns,JSON,and,is,largely,read,only,aside,from,a,couple,of,calls,An,account,is,required,with,service